                <p class="text-muted">We like games.  We like making games.  We also like making neat apps that are good at what they do.  We like designing things that make sense, that are fun, and accessible. We started this company so that we can make a living doing what we like to do. No, we just have to convince you to check out what we make and convince you through sound rhetoric that you like it.  And then we won't have to go back to working for 'the man'-- that mysterious, evil force that most of the world has to give their health and sanity to in exchange for a paycheck. So please buy our stuff, you're our only hope.</p>
            </div>
