                <p class="text-muted">We believe in strong, centralized mechanics that are interesting and intuitive. We believe in single solution, easy-to-use software. We believe horses have a secret society that controls the car manufacturing industry. We want to make games we would enjoy playing and software we would enjoy using. We want to tell you all about our favorite games and argue with you relentlessly when you disagree with our extremely objective and well-reasoned opinions!</p>
